THIS IS A WORK IN PROGRESS. Initial development is 
not complete.  Some parts of this block do not yet function.

This block wraps OpenNI for use with the Asus Xtion. 

This requires the PrimeSense driver, the OpenNI SDK, 
and the NITE SDK, which may be downloaded as a single 
installer here:
http://www.openni.org/openni-sdk/

